uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.tool.bean

Class GenericDiffBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.tool.bean.GenericDiffBean

  • public class GenericDiffBean
extends Object
    Bean Helper class that for creating diffs. Line endings for the left and right content are both normalized to Unix Line endings by the simple regular expression replace "\r\n?" with "\n"
    Version:
    $Id: GenericDiffBean.java 7664 2006-04-12 15:27:23Z ian@caret.cam.ac.uk $
    Author:
    andrew
